          <span class="arrow">+</span> Monthly digest
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <SectionHead marker="ABOUT THE AUTHOR" title="Harshith Kantamneni" level={3} />

  <div class="page-grid">
    <div class="extended measure-tight">
      <p>
        Builds and operates autonomous AI labs full-time. Currently running HIVE Product Lab and the Autonomous Research Lab.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

